Soothing and clear the notes of Color Me Sky Blue Deo Spray instantly chases away the blues of a Monday morning and fills your day with vibrant energy. For the woman who keeps up with the times and keeps herself updated on what’s hot and what’s not the mass premium fragrance lends a touch of glamor and a bit of color to her days. The deodorant spray with impressive longevity ensures that you do not have to bother about distasteful perspiration issues and odor-causing bacteria. As you dress for work or dress up for a fun girls’ night out Color Me Sky Blue adds the finishing touches to your perfect outfit with a flourish.

Made for use at any time of the day the fragrance of Sky Blue is a mild mix of citrus and succulence. The tangy accords of lemon lend their twang to the fragrance as it melts into the mouth watering lusciousness of ripe red cherries. Succulent and juicy peaches add their fuzzy softness to the mix along with the soothing sweetness of freesia which adds just a touch of honeyed lightness to the fragrance. The spray is presented in a simple flacon that reflects the name in color adding authenticity to the experience. Feel the notes of freedom from materialism flush through you with Colour Me Sky Blue Deo Spray the fragrance of the contemporary career woman.
